cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SY, cs.CV 

The paper discusses the use of deep reinforcement learning to improve evolutionary algorithms, which involves optimization and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also mentions the use of evolutionary algorithms in control systems (cs.SY) and optimization problems in computer vision (cs.CV), which are also possible categories.
